These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: juice, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
2. Beverage:juice is on the far right##1
3. Beverage:juice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | juice |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Music-Genre: reggae, disco, pop
1. Music-Genre:disco is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:reggae is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | pop | disco |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
City: hamburg, rome, miami
1. City:rome is in an even position##4
2. City:rome is on the left or right of City:miami##3
3. City:miami is on the right of City:rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| City   | hamburg | rome | miami |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
