.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
Birthday: february, january, september
1. Birthday:september is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:january == Birthday:january##1
3. Birthday:september is on the right of Birthday:january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | february | january | september |

